ISLAMABAD, Feb 2 (APP): Ahead of the Kashmir Solidarity Day, Additional Foreign Secretary (Asia & Pacific) Ambassador Imran Ahmed Siddiqui Friday briefed the Islamabad-based diplomats on the developments in the Indian Illegally Occupied Jammu and Kashmir (IIOJK).
He underscored the legal, security and human rights dimensions of the situation in IIOJK.
